main repo push

Push changes

USAGE:
    main repo push [OPTIONS] [REMOTE]

ARGUMENTS:
        <REMOTE>
            Remote name

OPTIONS:
    -h, --help
            Show help message and exit.
    -V, --version
            Show version and exit.
        --completions <bash,zsh,fish>
            Generate shell completions.
    -f, --force
            Force push
